Package: xiaomi-mipps-auth
Version: 0.21
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: arm64
Depends: python3, systemd, udev, util-linux, libglib2.0-bin
Maintainer: siergtc <i@4t.pw>
Description: Automatic Xiaomi MiPPS/PPS charger authentication for sheng
 Runs Xiaomi MiPPS authentication, with standard PPS fallback, when a compatible USB-C charger is attached.
